creator: lord android
descriptionHtml:
Latest Technology News Around The World in One Application.

- Choose and read the most famous Tech News blogs and sites with your mobile in the fastest way possible.
- If you want to stay up to date with what happens in the world of Technology, Hardware, smartphones, newest games and apps, updates and reviews, latest geek stories and use as little time as possible, then this app is what you need!

- Be first person who knows the latest tech news by this our app. All News are updated hourly. There is no need anymore to move between the different Tech sites on the internet browser or install the application for each site on your device or tire yourself in the search for the best articles you can read.
We have shorten  your time and we put all Technology Sites you favorite for one Application so you can now navigate between the Technology sites in easy way.


- A new application specially designed for those interested in technology news.

- Learn about the latest phones, applications, computers, internet news, games for Windows, Android and the latest smart watch releases. This application includes everything new in the world of technology and the latest news of electronic security.

- You can control the news display format Press Options and then change the layout.

- You can put your favorite news in your favorite news list.

- You can control the news update time.

- You can share your favorite news via social media sites.

- You can browse news without internet.

- You can search for any news you want.


- If you have any suggestion, type your comment.

If you like the application, please rate it with 5 stars 🤗
